# --- Source markdown (public PDF + internal references) -----------------
# These are the inputs to build_curated.py, not the output. They contain
# example license keys / node IDs / hashes that trigger secret scanners.
# Keep locally to drive the build; do not commit.
FortiSOAR-API-Guide.md

